      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Son with the Father by the Spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Conceived in a virgin’s womb"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The issue: a God-man, a wonderful Person,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus divine and human."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wonderful One, Son with the Father,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wonderful One, Son by the Spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wonderful Jesus Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wonderful Triune, Wonderful Triune God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This man in perfection chose God as His living;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He lived the life of God."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The sin, world, and Satan could not penetrate Him;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus had sinless blood."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Humanity, His blood has cleansed me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Divinity, my guarantee."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His sinless blood cleansed me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s now my guaran—, God’s now my guarantee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His flesh without sin joined man’s flesh full of sin"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And this trapped Satan."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Man’s flesh, sin and Satan were hanging upon Him"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O what a termination!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Terminating, the old creation,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nullifying, flesh, sin and Satan."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O what a promised seed!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He crushed the Devil’s, He crushed the Devil’s head."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in resurrection, this wonderful Person"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit He became."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit right now is the Son with the Father"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be the consummation."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wonderful One, life-giving Spirit!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Son has become the consummation."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Son with the Father, He"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As Spirit dwells in, as Spirit dwells in me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in His ascension, this wonderful Person,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This man is on God’s throne."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The highest position, to Him it was given,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s ruling and reigning."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As Lord of lords and King of kings,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The highest name to Jesus given."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This man is on God’s throne."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Most wonderful, most wonderful Person!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in His enthronement as Head over all things"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The processed God is He,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dispensing Himself as the life-giving Spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Producing His Body."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Triune God is not for doctrine."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Trinity is for dispensing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s now dispensing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we’re enjoying, and we’re enjoying Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
  ],
